## shared/ui Component Checklist (new atoms/molecules only)
- [ ] Polymorphic support (as prop)
- [ ] Variant/size/tone props
- [ ] Token-based styling
- [ ] ARIA attributes
- [ ] forwardRef
- [ ] TypeScript types
- [ ] Unit tests
- [ ] Storybook stories
- [ ] Exported from shared/ui/index.ts
